### GasStation Hub - HTTP Client Requests (API Gateway: 8080)

# =========================================================================
# 1. FLUXO DE FIDELIDADE (loyalty-service via Gateway)
# =========================================================================

### Consultar pontos de um cliente (cria registro padrão se não existir no MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/loyalty/12345/points
Accept: application/json


### Adicionar pontos diretamente a um cliente no MongoDB
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loyalty/12345/add-points?points=500
Accept: application/json


# =========================================================================
# 2. FLUXO DE ABASTECIMENTO (supply-service via Gateway)
# =========================================================================

### Realizar checkout de abastecimento (Persiste no Postgres + pontua no MongoDB)
# Se o loyalty-service estiver online: Conclui com sucesso e atualiza pontos.
# Se o loyalty-service estiver offline: Ativa o Circuit Breaker e executa o Fallback local.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/supplies/checkout?customerId=12345&amount=150.00&literage=25.0
Accept: application/json


### Realizar checkout com outros valores
POST http://localhost:8080/api/supplies/checkout?customerId=99999&amount=300.00&literage=50.0
Accept: application/json
